courses.course_syllabus:
(1) characteristics of the Chinese language environment in Hong Kong;    
(2) characteristics of ancient Chinese;    
(3) characteristics of modern Chinese;    
(4) reading of Ancient texts;    
(5) reading of modern texts;    
(6) writing in different geners.  
   
   
(1) 概述中文的特質與香港的語言環境；  
   
(2) 古代漢語的特點；  
   
(3) 現代漢語的特點；  
   
(4) 篇章選讀一﹕古代；  
   
(5) 篇章選讀二﹕現代；  
   
(6) 不同文體寫作

