courses.learning_outcomes:
修畢本科後，學生能︰

[1] 掌握基本漢語知識，準確運用詞語和句式；

[2] 掌握不同文類的閱讀策略；

[3] 掌握基本寫作技巧；

[4] 善用自學策略，提升語文能力。

Upon completion of the course, students will be able to:

[1] acquire basic language knowledge of Chinese and to apply the knowledge in appropriate contexts;

[2] acquire strategies for reading different text-type;

[3] acquire basic writing skills;

[4] improve the self-learning strategies to raise the language ability.

